{"type":"lrc","txt":"[00:00.000] \u4f5c\u8bcd : Jascha Richter\n[00:01.000] \u4f5c\u66f2 : Jascha Richter\n[00:10.050]Baby won't you tell me why there is sadness in your eyes\n[00:17.420]I don't wanna say goodbye to you\n[00:25.070]Love is one big illusion I should try to forget\n[00:32.520]but there is something left in my head\n[00:40.020]You're the one who set it up\n[00:43.020]Now you're the one to make it stop\n[00:47.570]I'm the one who's feeling lost right now\n[00:55.080]Now you want me to forget every little thing you said\n[01:02.580]but there is something left in my head\n[01:08.490]Chorus:I won't forget the way you're kissing\n[01:15.670]The feelings so strong were lasting for so long\n[01:23.260]But I'm not the man your heart is missing\n[01:30.960]That's why you go away I know\n[01:40.200]You were never satisfied no matter how I tried\n[01:47.780]Now you wanna say goodbye to me\n[01:55.250]Love is one big illusion I should try to forget\n[02:02.800]but there is something left in my head\n[02:08.690]Chorus:I won't forget the way you're kissing\n[02:15.910]The feelings so strong were lasting for so long\n[02:23.490]But I'm not the man your heart is missing\n[02:31.180]That's why you go away I know\n[02:40.370]Sitting here all alone in the middle of nowhere\n[02:48.500]Don't know which way to go\n[02:55.400]There ain't so much to say now between us\n[03:02.980]There ain't so much for you\n[03:06.690]There ain't so much for me anymore\n[03:27.850]Chorus:I won't forget the way you're kissing\n[03:34.880]The feelings so strong were lasting for so long\n[03:42.420]But I'm not the man your heart is missing\n[03:50.200]That's why you go away I know\n[03:57.990]That's why you go away I know\n"}